- **ğŸ›  Zero-Config C++ Setup:** Generates a production-ready structure (`src`, `include`, `build`) with Modern CMake configuration (C++17 standard).
- **ğŸ— Scalable Architecture:** Enforces separation of concerns immediately.
- **ğŸ Python Ready:** (Coming Soon in v0.2) Standardized templates for Python projects.
